first write command to enable nestjs-"npm i -g @nest.js/cli"
after it run command-"nest new api"
for run this project go to "cd api" and after it "npm run start"
add some pakages-"npm i @nestjs/typeorm typeorm" and "npm i pg @nestjs/config"
postgress detail for backend to database connection-
POSTGRESS_HOST=127.0.0.1
POSTGRESS_PORT=5432
POSTGRESS_USER=postgres
POSTGRESS_PASSWORD=Admin
POSTGRESS_DATABASE=linkedin
JWT_SECRET=jwtsecret
to generate the feed module run command- "nest g mo feed"
to generate the auth controller- nest g co auth/controllers/auth
to generate the feed service run command- nest g s feed/services/feed
npm i passport passport-jwt @nestjs/passport @nestjs/jwt bcrypt
to generate the guard- nest g gu auth/guards/jwt
to generate the decorator-nest g d auth/decorators/role